to group the users of your app,

1209
00:47:28,666 --> 00:47:32,686 A:middle
that particular audience, into
various categories depending

1210
00:47:32,686 --> 00:47:35,676 A:middle
on their activity within your
app, or things that you know

1211
00:47:35,676 --> 00:47:37,766 A:middle
about them from their
use of your app.

1212
00:47:39,706 --> 00:47:41,836 A:middle
This might be frequent
in-app purchases.

1213
00:47:42,496 --> 00:47:45,116 A:middle
It might be a very high
usage rate relative

1214
00:47:45,116 --> 00:47:46,426 A:middle
to other users within your app.

1215
00:47:47,016 --> 00:47:49,976 A:middle
It might be dormant users, users
who used your app a while ago

1216
00:47:49,976 --> 00:47:51,456 A:middle
but you haven't seen in a while.

1217
00:47:53,196 --> 00:47:56,696 A:middle
You can then use this
information to target new ads

1218
00:47:56,696 --> 00:48:01,086 A:middle
in iAd Workbench directly at
specific subgroups of your users

