00:49:24,296 --> 00:49:26,816 A:middle
Maybe you should come back
and reengage with this app.

1257
00:49:26,846 --> 00:49:28,556 A:middle
Maybe you still want to
purchase those things."

1258
00:49:29,346 --> 00:49:31,576 A:middle
If you've got loyal
customers maybe you want

1259
00:49:31,576 --> 00:49:32,536 A:middle
to send them a special offer.

1260
00:49:32,536 --> 00:49:34,686 A:middle
Maybe you want to send them a
